text: Eunidia naviauxi is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Villiers in 1977. It is known from Saudi Arabia, Djibouti, Yemen, Egypt, Chad, Oman, Niger, and Senegal.BioLib.cz - Eunidia naviauxi.
